    <item>
      <title>加密货币市场突破疫情时期峰值，比特币逼近 90,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/bitcoin-btc-record-lifts-crypto-market-value-past-pandemic-era-peak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币的创纪录上涨首次使该数字资产接近 90,000 美元，并将加密货币市场的整体价值推高至大流行时期的峰值以上，因为交易员押注当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 会带来繁荣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/bitcoin-btc-record-lifts-crypto-market-value-past-pandemic-era-peak</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 23:35:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西对冲基金 Verde 称其在特朗普获胜前押注比特币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/hedge-fund-verde-says-it-made-bitcoin-bet-before-trump-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由行业资深人士 Luis Stuhlberger 经营的巴西资产管理公司 Verde Asset Management 是受候任总统唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫所引发的比特币涨势的投资者之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/hedge-fund-verde-says-it-made-bitcoin-bet-before-trump-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 20:46:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比特币对冲基金的几乎无风险交易正在卷土重来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/bitcoin-hedge-funds-just-about-risk-free-trade-is-roaring-back</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币价格创纪录的迅猛上涨，使得加密对冲基金最受欢迎的交易之一比平时更加​​有利可图，并可能有助于推动原始数字货币达到曾经不可思议的高度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/bitcoin-hedge-funds-just-about-risk-free-trade-is-roaring-back</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 17:58:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
